items.sentence: Why do you think Tom would do something like that?
Why don't you come to my place for dinner tonight?
Why don't we go to the beach and watch the sunset?
Why do some people learn more quickly than others?
Why couldn't you just ask somebody for directions?
Things like that don't usually happen around here.
Tom is survived by his parents and three children.
I thought it sounded like Tom was speaking French.
Tom was handcuffed to the chair he was sitting on.
Tom lets his children do whatever they want to do.
